data.description: Built in 2017 newer construction w/ 9' ceilings and awesome open concept floor plan. Southern facing unit with loads of sunlight. One of the most upgraded units in the complex.   Vinyl plank lower level at Entry & Den/Office. Wood floors thru-out 2nd and 3rd floors and oak wood staircases. White kitchen with breakfast bar, granite countertops, SS appliances. Primary Bdrm Suite w/ large custom walk-in closet, custom built-in armoire, and full bath w/ marble countertops. 3rd Floor Laundry. Energy-Efficient Geothermal Heating & Cooling keeps monthly costs low. Attached 2 car garage and guest parking available. Great location overlooking Mason Park with tennis courts, playground, basketball courts and baseball field outside your front door. Walk to Metra, CTA-Purple Line, Schools and all downtown Evanston has to offer. Only 3 min drive/10 min bike ride to Clark Street Beach. Low taxes and low assessments. Just move right in and enjoy the holidays in this beautiful home!
